Output docs/media/oxdeai-demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Builtin Solarized Dark"
Set Margin 24

Type "echo Running OxDeAI adapter validation demo"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "pnpm validate:adapters"
Enter
Sleep 7s

Type "echo OxDeAI deterministic authorization boundary for agent actions"
Enter
Sleep 30s
